data.description: Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home with neutral paint and modern updates. As you enter the front door, you are greeted by an open concept common area with LVP. The split bedroom floorplan has 3 guest bedrooms down the hall to the right of the kitchen with a full bath. A second full bath sits off the dining and common areas. To the left is the master bedroom suite with open closet and large bathroom. Off the kitchen, to the back, is the covered back porch and fenced back yard. Seller will need possession after closing. Make this recently renovated, spacious home yours today!
